---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
const title = "Steyn et al. (2026) — Continuum reverberation in bright quasars";
import WikiLink from '../../components/WikiLink.astro';
---
<Base title={title}>
  <Sidebar />
  <main class="page-main">
    <h1 class="page-title">Steyn et al. (2026) — Continuum Reverberation in Bright Quasars</h1>

    <div class="infobox">
      <h3 class="infobox-title">Paper</h3>
      <table>
        <tr><th>Type:</th><td>Paper</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Authors:</th><td>Zachary Steyn et al.</td></tr>
        <tr><th>arXiv:</th><td><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.11789">2603.11789</a></td></tr>
        <tr><th>Submitted:</th><td>2026-03-12</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Abstract (short)</strong> — Joint lag fits across 9,498 bright quasars show the disk-size discrepancy persists; complex wavelength dependence suggests diffuse emission contamination. Lags correlate with Eddington ratio and other spectral properties.</p>

    <h2>Key claims</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Observed inter-band continuum lags remain ≈3× larger than thin-disk predictions even in luminous quasars.</li>
      <li>Wavelength effects and diffuse emission contamination drive complex lag behaviour and the apparent luminosity trends.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>See also</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><WikiLink slug="pages/continuum_reverberation" text="Continuum reverberation" /></li>
      <li><WikiLink slug="pages/accretion_disk_size_problem" text="Accretion disk size problem" /></li>
    </ul>

    <div class="references">
      <h2>References</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Steyn et al. (2026). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.11789">arXiv:2603.11789</a>.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
